00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:04.349
This type of,

00:02:04.349 --> 00:02:06.482
and actually it could
even be several genes

00:02:06.482 --> 00:02:07.736
that are involved in that type of food,

00:02:07.736 --> 00:02:10.374
and we will actually talk, go
into a little bit more detail

00:02:10.374 --> 00:02:12.791
about when you have several
genes that are related

00:02:12.791 --> 00:02:14.796
and they tend to be
transcribed all at once

00:02:14.796 --> 00:02:16.782
or not transcribed all at once.

00:02:16.782 --> 00:02:18.440
So maybe that's related to

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:21.501
digesting or consuming some type of food.

00:02:21.501 --> 00:02:24.795
Maybe you have some genes over here

00:02:24.795 --> 00:02:28.618
that are related to some
type of stress mechanism.

00:02:28.618 --> 00:02:31.684
Maybe it needs to go into
hibernation some time.

